#CHIP RF5C164
#CLOCK 7670453

; RF5C164 (Sega CD PCM) Pitch Tracking Test
;
; The RF5C164 supports pitch modulation of PCM samples.
; This test validates pitch sweep tracking and frequency modulation.
;
; Tests:
; - Pitch bend over sample range
; - Frequency modulation accuracy
; - Pitch register write timing

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Start with normal pitch
c4 .

; Pitch up (higher frequency)
d4 .

; Pitch down (lower frequency)
c4 .

r4

; Pitch sweep: ascending
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 .

r4

; Pitch sweep: descending
g4 . f4 . e4 . d4 .

r4

; Rapid pitch modulation
c4 . . d4 . . e4 . . f4 . .

r2

#END
